    "image": "icons/equipment/neck/amulet-carved-runed-othila-fehu-grey.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While you wear this amulet of silver and turquoise, you have advantage on saving throws against effects that turn &amp;Reference[undead]{undead}.</p>\n<p>If you fail a saving throw against such an effect, you can choose to succeed instead. You can do so three times, and expended uses recharge daily at dawn.</p>\n<p>Each time an effect that turns &amp;Reference[undead]{undead} is used against you, the amulet glows with silvery blue light for a few seconds.</p>\n</div>",
