    "rarity": "rare",
    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "icons/equipment/shield/oval-wooden-boss-bronze.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You gain a +2 bonus to AC against ranged attacks while you wield this shield. This bonus is in addition to the shield's normal bonus to AC. In addition, whenever an attacker makes a ranged attack against a target within 5 feet of you, you can use your reaction to become the target of the attack instead.</p>\n</div>",
