    "image": "icons/tools/instruments/chimes-wood-brown.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>If you have proficiency with a given musical instrument, you can add your proficiency bonus to any ability checks you make to play music with the instrument. A bard can use bagpipes as a spellcasting focus.</p>\n</div>",
