    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Banana.webp",
    "description": "<p>A fruit favored by most folk, herbalists recommend it if your stomach is upset, innkeepers provide it mushed as sweet beverages, and commoners eat it raw as it is quite tasty.</p><p></p>",
