    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You have a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.  <strong>T</strong>his axe is cursed and as soon as you attune to it the curse extends to you.  If you are hit while raging during combat you must roll a [[/save wis 15 format=long]].  If you fail you go into a blood-lust and must attack whichever creature is closest to you as long as you are in a blood-lust.  You can re-roll the saving throw at the beginning of each of your turns.</p>\n</div>",
