    "price": 3,
    "rarity": "common",
    "isMagic": false,
    "image": "icons/weapons/thrown/shuriken-double-red.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>The boomerang is a ranged weapon, and any creature proficient with the javelin is also proficient with this weapon.</p>\n<p>On a miss, a boomerang returns to the thrower's hand.</p>\n</div>",
