    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This bottle contains a breath of &amp;Reference[elemental]{elemental} air. When you inhale it, you either exhale it or hold it.</p>\n<p>If you exhale the breath, you gain the effect of the gust of wind spell. If you hold the breath, you don’t need to breathe for 1 hour, though you can end this benefit early (for example, to speak). Ending it early doesn’t give you the benefit of exhaling the breath.</p>\n</div>",
