    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While this bowl is filled with water, you can use an action to speak the bowl's command word and summon a water &amp;Reference[elemental]{elemental}, as if you had cast the conjure &amp;Reference[elemental]{elemental} spell. The bowl can't be used this way again until the next dawn.</p>\n<p>The bowl is about 1 foot in diameter and half as deep. It weighs 3 pounds and holds about 3 gallons.</p>\n</div>",
