    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While a &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} burns in this brass brazier, you can use an action to speak the brazier’s command word and summon a &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} &amp;Reference[elemental]{elemental}, as if you had cast the conjure &amp;Reference[elemental]{elemental} spell. The brazier can’t be used this way again until the next dawn.</p>\n<p>The brazier weighs 5 pounds.</p>\n</div>",
