    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While wearing this brooch, you have resistance to &amp;Reference[force]{force} damage, and you have immunity to damage from the @UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-my-first-world-ddb-spells.Item.766zwibausuyMPyI]{magic missile} spell.</p>\n</div>",
