    "description": "<p>Commonly known as Carnation or clove pink, and besides the ornamental aspect of them, where most houses have a potted flower. The Carnations, after turning in a paste with honey, are used by some herbalists to treat issues such as skin problems, hair loss, and muscle tension.</p>",
