    "description": "<p>Imagine a fresh-cut carp steak sizzling on the grill, the smoky aroma mixing with herbs and spices, or a baked fillet coming out of the oven golden brown, ready to be served with a side of roasted vegetables and a splash of lemon. This is the essence of carp: simple yet delicious, prepared fresh for every meal.</p>",
