    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>If you have proficiency with a certain kind of vehicle (land or water), you can add your proficiency bonus to any check you make to control that kind of vehicle in difficult circumstances.</p>\n</div>",
    "weight": 100,
    "folder": "Vehicle",
