    "rarity": "uncommon",
    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/6688948c1b83176d39831d47/ddb-images/other/item/equipment/Cloak-of-Elvenkind.jpeg",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While you wear this cloak with its hood up, &amp;Reference[wis]{Wisdom} (&amp;Reference[prc]{Perception}) checks made to see you have disadvantage, and you have advantage on &amp;Reference[dex]{Dexterity} (&amp;Reference[ste]{Stealth}) checks made to hide, as the cloak's color shifts to camouflage you. Pulling the hood up or down requires an action.</p>\n</div>",
