    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/6688948c1b83176d39831d47/ddb-images/other/item/equipment/Cloak-of-Many-Fashions.jpeg",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While wearing this cloak, you can use a bonus action to change the style, color, and apparent quality of the garment. The cloak’s weight doesn’t change. Regardless of its appearance, the cloak can’t be anything but a cloak. Although it can duplicate the appearance of other magic cloaks, it doesn’t gain their magical properties.</p>\n</div>",
