    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This elegant outfit of traveler’s clothes magically mends itself to counteract daily wear and tear. Pieces of the outfit that are destroyed can’t be repaired in<span class=\"No-Break\"> this way.</span></p>\n</div>",
