    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You have a +1 bonus to AC while wearing this armor.</p>\n<p>This +1 breastplate has a gold &amp;Reference[dragon]{dragon} motif worked into its design. Created for a human hero of Neverwinter named Tergon, it grants its wearer advantage on saving throws against the breath weapons of creatures that have the &amp;Reference[dragon]{dragon} type.</p>\n</div>",
