    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Eggs%20Rice%20and%20Green%20Beans.webp",
    "description": "<p>A very hearty meal, the eggs complement the rice well, and the rice pairs wonderfully with the beans. This dish comes highly recommended by most tavern keepers.</p><p></p>",
