    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>When you attain rank 4, you gain a small tome that is an uncommon magic item. The <em>elder cartographer’s glossography</em> grants advantage on &amp;Reference[int]{Intelligence} or &amp;Reference[wis]{Wisdom} checks related to geographical features or locations.</p>\n</div>",
