    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/6688948c1b83176d39831d47/ddb-images/other/item/equipment/Gauntlets-of-Ogre-Power.jpeg",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>Your &amp;Reference[str]{Strength} score is 19 while you wear these gauntlets. They have no effect on you if your &amp;Reference[str]{Strength} is 19 or higher without them.</p>\n</div>",
