    "description": "<p><span style=\"font-family:serif\">A famous vintage of red wine with a bouquet that is aromatic, green, and full.<br style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:serif;font-size:19.2px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:center;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 221);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></span></p>",
