    "type": "equipment",
    "price": 100,
    "rarity": "common",
    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "icons/commodities/bones/horn-jagged-gold.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This horn has 4 charges. When you use an action to blow it, one creature of your choice can hear the horn’s blare, provided the creature is within 600 feet of the horn and not &amp;Reference[deafened]{deafened}. No other creature hears sound coming from the horn. The horn regains 1d4 expended charges dail<span class=\"No-Break\">y at dawn.</span></p>\n</div>",
