    "price": 100,
    "rarity": "common",
    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "icons/sundries/misc/lock-steel-blue.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This lock appears to be an ordinary lock (of the type described in chapter 5 of the <span class=\"Serif-Character-Style_Italic-Serif\">Player’s Handbook</span>) and comes with a single key. The tumblers in this lock magically adjust to thwart burglars. &amp;Reference[dex]{Dexterity} checks made to pick the lock have dis<span class=\"No-Break\">advantage.</span></p>\n</div>",
