    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While wearing this armor, you have a swimming speed equal to your walking speed. In addition, whenever you start your turn underwater with 0 hit points, the armor causes you to rise 60 feet toward the surface. The armor is decorated with fish and she<span class=\"No-Break\">ll motifs.</span></p>\n</div>",
