    "image": "icons/consumables/potions/potion-flask-corked-labeled-pink.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This tiny vial contains magic perfume, enough for one use. You can use an action to apply the perfume to yourself, and its effect lasts 1 hour. For the duration, you have advantage on all &amp;Reference[cha]{Charisma} checks directed at humanoids of challenge rating 1 or lower. Those subjected to the perfume’s effect are not aware that they’ve been influenced<span class=\"No-Break\"> by magic.</span></p>\n</div>",
