    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This delicate silver chain has a brilliant-cut black gem pendant. While you wear it, poisons have no effect on you. You are immune to the &amp;Reference[poisoned]{poisoned} condition and have immunity to &amp;Reference[poison]{poison} damage.</p>\n</div>",
