    "price": 1500,
    "rarity": "common",
    "isMagic": false,
    "image": "icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-layered-steel-black.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>Plate consists of shaped, interlocking metal plates to cover the entire body. A suit of plate includes gauntlets, heavy leather boots, a visored helmet, and thick layers of padding underneath the armor. Buckles and straps distribute the weight over the body.</p>\n</div>",
    "weight": 65,
