    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While holding this 10-foot pole, you can speak a command word and transform it into a fishing pole with a hook, a &amp;Reference[line]{line}, and a reel. Speaking the command word again changes the fishing pole back into a normal 10-<span class=\"No-Break\">foot pole.</span></p>\n</div>",
