    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "icons/containers/kitchenware/pot-meal.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">If you &amp;Reference[plant]{plant} an ordinary shrub in this 10-pound clay pot and let it grow for 30 days, the shrub magically transforms into an <span class=\"Serif-Character-Style_Bold-Serif\">awakened shrub</span> at the end of that time. When the shrub awakens, its roots break the pot, dest<span class=\"No-Break\">roying it.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">The awakened shrub is friendly toward you. Absent commands from you, it doe<span class=\"No-Break\">s nothing.</span></p>\n</div>",
