    "isMagic": false,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Rutile%20Powder.webp",
    "description": "<p>Rutile when ground into a fine powder, it turns into a beautiful pigment, bringing color to canvases and ceramics alike. In the world of medicine, its strength and resistance to corrosion make it a primary material, protecting implants and ensuring their longevity. </p>",
