    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/6688948c1b83176d39831d47/ddb-images/other/ddb/item/ring.jpg",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<div class=\"item-attunement\"><i>(Requires attunement by a Spellcaster)</i></div><p>This gilded ring bears a beautiful engraving and is imbued with powers of keen wisdom and foresight. While wearing this ring, you can use an action to cast the Augury spell from the ring. Once you use the ring to cast the spell, the ring can’t cast the spell again until the next dawn.</p>\n<p>While wearing the <em>Sage’s Signet</em>, you can cast Fear and Hex once each from the ring using your Intelligence as the spellcasting ability. Once you cast each of the additional spells from the ring, it can’t cast the spell again until the next dawn.</p>\n</div>",
