    "type": "weapon",
    "price": 5000,
    "rarity": "rare",
    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "icons/weapons/swords/scimitar-bone.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>When you attack a creature with this magic weapon and roll a 20 on the attack roll, that target takes an extra 10 &amp;Reference[necrotic]{necrotic} damage if it isn't a &amp;Reference[construct]{construct} or an &amp;Reference[undead]{undead}. You also gain 10 temporary hit points.</p>\n</div>",
