    "image": "icons/equipment/shield/oval-wooden-boss-steel.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>A shield is made from wood or metal and is carried in one hand. Wielding a shield increases your Armor Class by 2. You can benefit from only one shield at a time.</p>\n</div>",
