    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/6688948c1b83176d39831d47/ddb-images/other/item/equipment/Shield-of-Missile-Attraction.jpeg",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While holding this shield, you have resistance to damage from ranged weapon attacks.</p>\n<p><strong>Curse.</strong> This shield is cursed. Attuning to it curses you until you are targeted by the @UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-my-first-world-ddb-spells.Item.VxP4c5gEjDSJHX33]{remove curse} spell or similar magic. Removing the shield fails to end the curse on you. Whenever a ranged weapon attack is made against a target within 10 feet of you, the curse causes you to become the target instead.</p>\n</div>",
    "weight": 6,
