    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>Ammunition fired from this bow blazes brightly. When you hit with an attack roll using this bow, the target takes an extra  [[/damage 1d6 type=fire average=true]] damage. If the target is a flammable, nonmagical object, it catches fire, taking  [[/damage 1d6 type=fire average=true]] damage at the start of each of your turns until a creature uses an action to extinguish the flames.</p>\n</div>",
