    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Spinach.webp",
    "description": "<p>Its leaves are a common edible vegetable consumed fresh, stir-fried, or steamed. Herbalists use wine fortified with spinach juice to give to the injured with the intent of reducing or stopping bleeding.</p><p></p>",
    "weight": 1,
