    "isMagic": false,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Spinning%20Wheel.webp",
    "description": "<p>A spinning wheel, or spindle, is a mechanical device used for spinning thread or yarn from fibers. It converts raw materials such as wool or cotton into usable thread through a process of twisting and winding, which is integral to fabric creation.</p>",
