    "image": "icons/commodities/materials/plant-branch-brown-green.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>A druid can use a Sprig of Mistletoe (or holly) as a spellcasting focus, as described in the <a href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/spellcasting#MaterialM\">Spellcasting</a> section.</p>\n</div>",
