    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/6688948c1b83176d39831d47/ddb-images/other/item/equipment/Stone-of-Controlling-Earth-Elementals.jpeg",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>If the stone is touching the ground, you can use an action to speak its command word and summon an earth &amp;Reference[elemental]{elemental}, as if you had cast the <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-my-first-world-ddb-spells.Item.P4aRQRxDmZz6VEIJ]{conjure elemental} spell. The stone can't be used this way again until the next dawn. The stone weighs 5 pounds.</p>\n</div>",
