    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Sugar%20Pumpkin.webp",
    "description": "<p>Sugar pumpkins are a type of winter squash recognized for their sweet flavor and firm, smooth, dense flesh, making them perfect for pumpkin pies and other baked goods like cookies and loaves of bread.</p><p></p>",
