    "isMagic": false,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Toy%20Horse.webp",
    "description": "<p>The toy horse provides a sense of adventure for young children, crafted primarily from wood and often accompanied by wooden toy swords and shields. It sparks the imagination and is a must for the new aspiring adventurers.</p><p></p>",
    "weight": 2,
    "folder": "Carpentry",
