    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This trident is a magic weapon. It has 3 charges. While you carry it, you can use an action and expend 1 charge to cast <strong></strong><strong>dominate &amp;Reference[beast]{beast}</strong> (save DC 15) from it on a &amp;Reference[beast]{beast} that has an innate swimming speed. The trident regains 1d3 expended charges daily at dawn.</p>\n</div>",
