    "isMagic": false,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Tuna%20Fish.webp",
    "description": "<p>The tuna is a saltwater fish, commonly found in warmer waters across the realms. It is widely harvested from the seas and oceans, with catches often reaching hundreds of pounds or more per fish, making it a valuable resource in many regions.</p>",
    "weight": 25,
    "folder": "Food",
    "stats": {}
