    "price": 5000,
    "rarity": "rare",
    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/6688948c1b83176d39831d47/ddb-images/other/item/consumable/Wand-of-Fireballs.jpeg",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<div class=\"item-attunement\"><i>(Requires attunement by a Spellcaster)</i></div><p>This wand has 7 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast the <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-my-first-world-ddb-spells.Item.JTgaByMqgBqbP2ag]{fireball} spell (save DC 15) from it. For 1 charge, you cast the 3rd-level version of the spell. You can increase the spell slot level by one for each additional charge you expend.</p>\n<p>The wand regains 1d6 + 1 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the wand crumbles into ashes and is destroyed.</p>\n</div>",
