    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While holding this fan, you can use an action to cast the <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-my-first-world-ddb-spells.Item.eB7pngCCbMCelsjq]{gust of wind} spell (save DC 13) from it. Once used, the fan shouldn't be used again until the next dawn. Each time it is used again before then, it has a cumulative 20 percent chance of not working and tearing into useless, nonmagical tatters.</p>\n</div>",
