    "rarity": "rare",
    "isMagic": true,
    "image": "icons/weapons/axes/axe-broad-purple.webp",
    "description": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You have a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.</p>\n<p>When you use this axe to make an attack against a &amp;Reference[plant]{plant} (an ordinary &amp;Reference[plant]{plant} or a creature with the &amp;Reference[plant]{Plant} type) or a wooden object that isn’t being worn or carried, the attack deals an extra  [[/damage 2d6 type=slashing average=true]] damage on a hit.</p>\n</div>",
