    "isMagic": false,
    "image": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/modules/kctg-5e/assets/images/Zither.webp",
    "description": "<p>The zither is an instrument that exists in various shapes and sizes, with the defining characteristic of being a plucked instrument. Numerous regional variations can be found worldwide. In some cultures, the zither is celebrated as an all-rounded instrument, valued for its beautiful and resonant sound. This instrument is not only a staple in music but is also well-regarded in some religious settings, where its beautiful sound enhances choir performances.</p>",
